## View vs Table Decision Matrix

**Use VIEW when:**
- Simple transformations
- Source data changes frequently
- Low query volume
- Storage optimization important

**Use TABLE when:**
- Complex window functions
- High query volume
- Source rarely changes
- Query performance critical
- Downstream models join to it

**Use EPHEMERAL when:**
- Only one downstream model
- Very simple transformation
- Want to avoid clutter

